title: Person of Interest || "Are you abducting someone?"
author: little carpenter
comment: I love the fact that everytime reese smiles is when you really need to start worrying
Am I the only one who loves John's smile right before he hits someone?

Amazing tribute.
For a show that's doing a ton of serious stuff and raising decently serious questions , PoI's humor is one of the best i've seen on TV.
I love the one at the end when Reese finds out why all the women keep slapping him.

The one that gets me everytime is when reese pushes a guy with a gun out of a window and he jumps wit him landing on a car. Everyone looks at him like " Are you crazy?"  he just shrugs like saying " what?"
